<br>
Put something like a Shissar fang in your ranged slot<br>
Summon some daggers with a Mrylokar bracer and put them in your ammo slot.<br>
<br>
Throw the summoned daggers as though they have the range of the shissar fang.  Exploit?  Maybe, but dang conovienent.  This works with pretty much anything.  I'm not sure if it works with archery or not, but basically the system checks your ranged slot for the stats and uses the ammo slot item first. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ukaaillasra.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kaail Lasra</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/30/02 5:48:04 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10879.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: summon item</span><hr size=1> Right now, Archery owns throwing very much bad. <br>
